<item>
            <title>[LU-18782] kernel update [RHEL 8.10 4.18.0-553.42.1.el8_10]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18782</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;virtio-net virtqueue causing stalled socket (JIRA:RHEL-72886)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;System hang due to soft lockup during snapshot removal with large hash list traversal in dm_exception_table_exit() &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;rhel-8.10.z&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (JIRA:RHEL-76230)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RHEL-8&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Lots of tasks are getting stuck in rwsem wait where the rwsem owner is calling throttle_direct_reclaim() and waiting (JIRA:RHEL-64950)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Alibaba&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Network PPS(Package Per Second) fails to meet the declared value in Spec against Gen8 AMD instance families on RHEL8.10 (JIRA:RHEL-66261)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RHEL-8.10z&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; rping loopback test over vlan fails to run (JIRA:RHEL-75826)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel panic in ovl_dentry_upper() due to null pointer dereference (JIRA:RHEL-76161)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;RHEL8.10 : Tapes are broken again on newest RHEL8.10 kernels - kernel-4.18.0-553.36.1.el8_10, RHEL9.5+ affected too (JIRA:RHEL-78415)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;NFS server thread blocked in flush_workqueue() (JIRA:RHEL-79458)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---8/x86_64/RHBA-2025:2352&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---8/x86_64/RHBA-2025:2352&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
